div.h1: x86 Boot Sequence: BIOS Kernel Main
div.h2: The Handoff Chain from Power-On to C Entry

div.p: 16-bit Real Mode asm cli xor ax, ax mov ds, ax mov es, ax mov ss, ax mov sp, 0x7C00 sti
Global Descriptor Table asm lgdt [gdt_descriptor] 5 entries: Null, KCode, KData, UCode, UData
Set CR0.PE = 1 asm mov eax, cr0 or eax, 1 mov cr0, eax Warning: CPU now in "weird" state
Reload All Segments asm mov ax, 0x10 ; KData mov ds, ax mov es, ax mov fs, ax mov gs, ax mov ss, ax mov esp, 0x90000
Assembly Entry Point asm kernel_entry: mov esp, 0x200000 ; Stack cld ; Clear DF ; Zero BSS section mov edi, __bss_start mov ecx, __bss_end sub ecx, edi xor eax, eax rep stosb call kernel_main
